lang_des.chinesesimplified: 红虫是摇蚊幼虫，在积水的淤泥中度过了整个短暂的生命周期，因此一般在水塘淤泥中收集红虫。红虫极难保存，所以很难大量收集它们以供将来使用。
lang_des.english: Bloodworms (the larvae of chironomid midges) spend their entire brief life cycle in waterlogged mud of ponds and marshes. Due to their extreme perishability, large-scale collection and storage for future use proves exceptionally challenging.
